 368                                                                                                          
 369     @Override                                                                                            
 370     public List<DiscreteOrderItem> getDiscreteOrderItems() {                                             
 371         List<DiscreteOrderItem> discreteOrderItems = new ArrayList<DiscreteOrderItem>();                 
 372         for (FulfillmentGroupItem fgItem : fulfillmentGroupItems) {                                      
 373             OrderItem orderItem = fgItem.getOrderItem();                                                 
 374             if (orderItem instanceof BundleOrderItem) {                                                  
 375                 BundleOrderItemImpl bundleOrderItem = (BundleOrderItemImpl)orderItem;                    
 376                 for (DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem : bundleOrderItem.getDiscreteOrderItems()) {    
 377                     discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                           
 378                 }                                                                                        
 379             } else if (orderItem instanceof DiscreteOrderItem) {                                         
 380                 DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem = (DiscreteOrderItem)orderItem;                      
 381                 discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                               
 382             }                                                                                            
 383         }                                                                                                
 384         return discreteOrderItems;                                                                       
 385     }                                                                                                    
 386                                                                                                          
 387     @Override                                                                                            
 388     public void setFulfillmentGroupItems(List<FulfillmentGroupItem> fulfillmentGroupItems) {             
 389         this.fulfillmentGroupItems = fulfillmentGroupItems;                                              
 390     }                                                                                                    
 391                                                                                                          
 392     @Override                                                                                            
 393     public void addFulfillmentGroupItem(FulfillmentGroupItem fulfillmentGroupItem) {                     
 394         if (this.fulfillmentGroupItems == null) {                                                        
 395             this.fulfillmentGroupItems = new Vector<FulfillmentGroupItem>();                             
 396         }                                                                                                
 397         this.fulfillmentGroupItems.add(fulfillmentGroupItem);                                            
 398                                                                                                          
 399     }

 828     @Override                                                                                            
 829     public boolean equals(Object obj) {                                                                  
 830         if (this == obj) {                                                                               
 831             return true;                                                                                 
 832         }                                                                                                
 833         if (obj == null) {                                                                               
 834             return false;                                                                                
 835         }                                                                                                
 836         if (!getClass().isAssignableFrom(obj.getClass())) {                                              
 837             return false;                                                                                
 838         }                                                                                                
 839         FulfillmentGroupImpl other = (FulfillmentGroupImpl) obj;                                         
 840                                                                                                          
 841         if (id != null && other.id != null) {                                                            
 842             return id.equals(other.id);                                                                  
 843         }                                                                                                
 844                                                                                                          
 845         if (address == null) {                                                                           
 846             if (other.address != null) {                                                                 
 847                 return false;                                                                            
 848             }                                                                                            
 849         } else if (!address.equals(other.address)) {                                                     
 850             return false;                                                                                
 851         }                                                                                                
 852         if (fulfillmentGroupItems == null) {                                                             
 853             if (other.fulfillmentGroupItems != null) {                                                   
 854                 return false;                                                                            
 855             }                                                                                            
 856         } else if (!fulfillmentGroupItems.equals(other.fulfillmentGroupItems)) {                         
 857             return false;                                                                                
 858         }                                                                                                
 859         return true;                                                                                     
 860     }

1279     @Override                                                                                           
1280     public List<DiscreteOrderItem> getDiscreteOrderItems() {                                            
1281         List<DiscreteOrderItem> discreteOrderItems = new ArrayList<DiscreteOrderItem>();                
1282         for (FulfillmentGroupItem fgItem : fulfillmentGroupItems) {                                     
1283             OrderItem orderItem = fgItem.getOrderItem();                                                
1284             if (orderItem instanceof BundleOrderItem) {                                                 
1285                 BundleOrderItemImpl bundleOrderItem = (BundleOrderItemImpl)orderItem;                   
1286                 for (DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem : bundleOrderItem.getDiscreteOrderItems()) {   
1287                     discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                          
1288                 }                                                                                       
1289             } else if (orderItem instanceof DiscreteOrderItem) {                                        
1290                 DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem = (DiscreteOrderItem)orderItem;                     
1291                 discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                              
1292             }                                                                                           
1293         }                                                                                               
1294         return discreteOrderItems;                                                                      
1295     }                                                                                                   
1296                                                                                                         
1297     @Override                                                                                           
1298     public void setFulfillmentGroupItems(List<FulfillmentGroupItem> fulfillmentGroupItems) {            
1299         this.fulfillmentGroupItems = fulfillmentGroupItems;                                             
1300     }

1738     @Override                                                                                           
1739     public boolean equals(Object obj) {                                                                 
1740         if (this == obj) {                                                                              
1741             return true;                                                                                
1742         }                                                                                               
1743         if (obj == null) {                                                                              
1744             return false;                                                                               
1745         }                                                                                               
1746         if (!getClass().isAssignableFrom(obj.getClass())) {                                             
1747             return false;                                                                               
1748         }                                                                                               
1749         FulfillmentGroupImpl other = (FulfillmentGroupImpl) obj;                                        
1750                                                                                                         
1751         if (id != null && other.id != null) {                                                           
1752             return id.equals(other.id);                                                                 
1753         }                                                                                               
1754                                                                                                         
1755         if (address == null) {                                                                          
1756             if (other.address != null) {                                                                
1757                 return false;                                                                           
1758             }                                                                                           
1759         } else if (!address.equals(other.address)) {                                                    
1760             return false;                                                                               
1761         }                                                                                               
1762         if (fulfillmentGroupItems == null) {                                                            
1763             if (other.fulfillmentGroupItems != null) {                                                  
1764                 return false;                                                                           
1765             }                                                                                           
1766         } else if (!fulfillmentGroupItems.equals(other.fulfillmentGroupItems)) {                        
1767             return false;                                                                               
1768         }                                                                                               
1769         return true;                                                                                    
1770     }

2191         List<DiscreteOrderItem> discreteOrderItems = new ArrayList<DiscreteOrderItem>();                
2192         for (FulfillmentGroupItem fgItem : fulfillmentGroupItems) {                                     
2193             OrderItem orderItem = fgItem.getOrderItem();                                                
2194             if (orderItem instanceof BundleOrderItem) {                                                 
2195                 BundleOrderItemImpl bundleOrderItem = (BundleOrderItemImpl)orderItem;                   
2196                 for (DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem : bundleOrderItem.getDiscreteOrderItems()) {   
2197                     discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                          
2198                 }                                                                                       
2199             } else if (orderItem instanceof DiscreteOrderItem) {                                        
2200                 DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem = (DiscreteOrderItem)orderItem;                     
2201                 discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                              
2202             }                                                                                           
2203         }                                                                                               
2204         return discreteOrderItems;                                                                      
2205     }

 368     @Override                                                                                            
 369     public List<DiscreteOrderItem> getDiscreteOrderItems() {                                             
 370         List<DiscreteOrderItem> discreteOrderItems = new ArrayList<DiscreteOrderItem>();                 
 371         for (FulfillmentGroupItem fgItem : fulfillmentGroupItems) {                                      
 372             OrderItem orderItem = fgItem.getOrderItem();                                                 
 373             if (orderItem instanceof BundleOrderItem) {                                                  
 374                 BundleOrderItemImpl bundleOrderItem = (BundleOrderItemImpl)orderItem;                    
 375                 for (DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem : bundleOrderItem.getDiscreteOrderItems()) {    
 376                     discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                           
 377                 }                                                                                        
 378             } else if (orderItem instanceof DiscreteOrderItem) {                                         
 379                 DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem = (DiscreteOrderItem)orderItem;                      
 380                 discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                               
 381             }                                                                                            
 382         }                                                                                                
 383         return discreteOrderItems;                                                                       
 384     }                                                                                                    
 385

 502     @Override                                                                                            
 503     public List<FulfillmentGroupAdjustment> getFutureCreditFulfillmentGroupAdjustments() {               
 504         List<FulfillmentGroupAdjustment> futureCreditAdjustments = new ArrayList<>();                    
 505         for (FulfillmentGroupAdjustment adjustment : fulfillmentGroupAdjustments) {                      
 506             if (adjustment.isFutureCredit()) {                                                           
 507                 futureCreditAdjustments.add(adjustment);                                                 
 508             }                                                                                            
 509                                                                                                          
 510         }                                                                                                
 511         return futureCreditAdjustments;                                                                  
 512     }

 514     @Override                                                                                            
 515     public Money getFulfillmentGroupAdjustmentsValue() {                                                 
 516         Money adjustmentsValue = BroadleafCurrencyUtils.getMoney(BigDecimal.ZERO, getOrder().getCurrency(ðŸ”µ
 517         for (FulfillmentGroupAdjustment adjustment : fulfillmentGroupAdjustments) {                      
 518             if (!adjustment.isFutureCredit()) {                                                          
 519                 adjustmentsValue = adjustmentsValue.add(adjustment.getValue());                          
 520             }                                                                                            
 521         }                                                                                                
 522         return adjustmentsValue;                                                                         
 523     }                                                                                                    
 524                                                                                                          
 525     @Override                                                                                            
 526     public Money getFutureCreditFulfillmentGroupAdjustmentsValue() {                                     
 527         Money adjustmentsValue = BroadleafCurrencyUtils.getMoney(BigDecimal.ZERO, getOrder().getCurrency(ðŸ”µ
 528         for (FulfillmentGroupAdjustment adjustment : getFutureCreditFulfillmentGroupAdjustments()) {     
 529             adjustmentsValue = adjustmentsValue.add(adjustment.getValue());                              
 530         }                                                                                                
 531         return adjustmentsValue;                                                                         
 532     }

 827     @Override                                                                                            
 828     public boolean equals(Object obj) {                                                                  
 829         if (this == obj) {                                                                               
 830             return true;                                                                                 
 831         }                                                                                                
 832         if (obj == null) {                                                                               
 833             return false;                                                                                
 834         }                                                                                                
 835         if (!getClass().isAssignableFrom(obj.getClass())) {                                              
 836             return false;                                                                                
 837         }                                                                                                
 838         FulfillmentGroupImpl other = (FulfillmentGroupImpl) obj;                                         
 839                                                                                                          
 840         if (id != null && other.id != null) {                                                            
 841             return id.equals(other.id);                                                                  
 842         }                                                                                                
 843                                                                                                          
 844         if (address == null) {                                                                           
 845             if (other.address != null) {                                                                 
 846                 return false;                                                                            
 847             }                                                                                            
 848         } else if (!address.equals(other.address)) {                                                     
 849             return false;                                                                                
 850         }                                                                                                
 851         if (fulfillmentGroupItems == null) {                                                             
 852             if (other.fulfillmentGroupItems != null) {                                                   
 853                 return false;                                                                            
 854             }                                                                                            
 855         } else if (!fulfillmentGroupItems.equals(other.fulfillmentGroupItems)) {                         
 856             return false;                                                                                
 857         }                                                                                                
 858         return true;                                                                                     
 859     }

 268     @Override                                                                                            
 269     public List<DiscreteOrderItem> getDiscreteOrderItems() {                                             
 270         List<DiscreteOrderItem> discreteOrderItems = new ArrayList<DiscreteOrderItem>();                 
 271         for (FulfillmentGroupItem fgItem : fulfillmentGroupItems) {                                      
 272             OrderItem orderItem = fgItem.getOrderItem();                                                 
 273             if (orderItem instanceof BundleOrderItem) {                                                  
 274                 BundleOrderItemImpl bundleOrderItem = ((BundleOrderItemImpl) (orderItem));               
 275                 for (DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem : bundleOrderItem.getDiscreteOrderItems()) {    
 276                     discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                           
 277                 }                                                                                        
 278             } else if (orderItem instanceof DiscreteOrderItem) {                                         
 279                 DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem = ((DiscreteOrderItem) (orderItem));                 
 280                 discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                               
 281             }                                                                                            
 282         }                                                                                                
 283         return discreteOrderItems;                                                                       
 284     }                                                                                                    
 285

 404     public List<FulfillmentGroupAdjustment> getFutureCreditFulfillmentGroupAdjustments() {               
 405         List<FulfillmentGroupAdjustment> futureCreditAdjustments = new ArrayList<>();                    
 406         for (FulfillmentGroupAdjustment adjustment : fulfillmentGroupAdjustments) {                      
 407             if (adjustment.isFutureCredit()) {

 409             }                                                                                            
 410         }                                                                                                
 411         return futureCreditAdjustments;                                                                  
 412     }

 414     @Override                                                                                            
 415     public Money getFulfillmentGroupAdjustmentsValue() {                                                 
 416         Money adjustmentsValue = BroadleafCurrencyUtils.getMoney(BigDecimal.ZERO, getOrder().getCurrency(ðŸ”µ
 417         for (FulfillmentGroupAdjustment adjustment : fulfillmentGroupAdjustments) {                      
 418             if (!adjustment.isFutureCredit()) {                                                          
 419                 adjustmentsValue = adjustmentsValue.add(adjustment.getValue());                          
 420             }                                                                                            
 421         }                                                                                                
 422         return adjustmentsValue;                                                                         
 423     }                                                                                                    
 424                                                                                                          
 425     @Override                                                                                            
 426     public Money getFutureCreditFulfillmentGroupAdjustmentsValue() {                                     
 427         Money adjustmentsValue = BroadleafCurrencyUtils.getMoney(BigDecimal.ZERO, getOrder().getCurrency(ðŸ”µ
 428         for (FulfillmentGroupAdjustment adjustment : getFutureCreditFulfillmentGroupAdjustments()) {     
 429             adjustmentsValue = adjustmentsValue.add(adjustment.getValue());                              
 430         }                                                                                                
 431         return adjustmentsValue;                                                                         
 432     }

 370      @Override                                                                                                     
 371      public List<DiscreteOrderItem> getDiscreteOrderItems() {                                                      
 372          List<DiscreteOrderItem> discreteOrderItems = new ArrayList<DiscreteOrderItem>();                          
 373          for (FulfillmentGroupItem fgItem : fulfillmentGroupItems) {                                               
 374              OrderItem orderItem = fgItem.getOrderItem();                                                          
 375              if (orderItem instanceof BundleOrderItem) {                                                           
 376                  BundleOrderItemImpl bundleOrderItem = (BundleOrderItemImpl)orderItem;                             
 377                  for (DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem : bundleOrderItem.getDiscreteOrderItems()) {             
 378                      discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                                    
 379                  }                                                                                                 
 380              } else if (orderItem instanceof DiscreteOrderItem) {                                                  
 381                  DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem = (DiscreteOrderItem)orderItem;                               
 382                  discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                                        
 383              }                                                                                                     
 384          }                                                                                                         
 385          return discreteOrderItems;                                                                                
 386      }

 504      @Override                                                                                                     
 505      public List<FulfillmentGroupAdjustment> getFutureCreditFulfillmentGroupAdjustments() {                        
 506          List<FulfillmentGroupAdjustment> futureCreditAdjustments = new ArrayList<>();                             
 507          for (FulfillmentGroupAdjustment adjustment : fulfillmentGroupAdjustments) {                               
 508              if (adjustment.isFutureCredit()) {                                                                    
 509                  futureCreditAdjustments.add(adjustment);                                                          
 510              }                                                                                                     
 511                                                                                                                    
 512          }                                                                                                         
 513          return futureCreditAdjustments;                                                                           
 514      }

 516      @Override                                                                                                     
 517      public Money getFulfillmentGroupAdjustmentsValue() {                                                          
 518          Money adjustmentsValue = BroadleafCurrencyUtils.getMoney(BigDecimal.ZERO, getOrder().getCurrency());      
 519          for (FulfillmentGroupAdjustment adjustment : fulfillmentGroupAdjustments) {                               
 520              if (!adjustment.isFutureCredit()) {                                                                   
 521                  adjustmentsValue = adjustmentsValue.add(adjustment.getValue());                                   
 522              }                                                                                                     
 523          }                                                                                                         
 524          return adjustmentsValue;                                                                                  
 525      }                                                                                                             
 526                                                                                                                    
 527      @Override                                                                                                     
 528      public Money getFutureCreditFulfillmentGroupAdjustmentsValue() {                                              
 529          Money adjustmentsValue = BroadleafCurrencyUtils.getMoney(BigDecimal.ZERO, getOrder().getCurrency());      
 530          for (FulfillmentGroupAdjustment adjustment : getFutureCreditFulfillmentGroupAdjustments()) {              
 531              adjustmentsValue = adjustmentsValue.add(adjustment.getValue());                                       
 532          }                                                                                                         
 533          return adjustmentsValue;                                                                                  
 534      }

 777          this.shippingOverride = shippingOverride;                                                                 
 778      }

 780      @Override                                                                                                     
 781      public int hashCode() {                                                                                       
 782          final int prime = 31;                                                                                     
 783          int result = 1;                                                                                           
 784          result = prime * result + ((address == null) ? 0 : address.hashCode());                                   
 785          result = prime * result + ((fulfillmentGroupItems == null) ? 0 : fulfillmentGroupItems.hashCode());       
 786          return result;                                                                                            
 787      }

 789      @Override                                                                                                     
 790      public <G extends FulfillmentGroup> CreateResponse<G> createOrRetrieveCopyInstance(MultiTenantCopyContext contðŸ”µ
 791          CreateResponse<G> createResponse = context.createOrRetrieveCopyInstance(this);                            
 792          if (createResponse.isAlreadyPopulated()) {                                                                
 793              return createResponse;                                                                                
 794          }                                                                                                         
 795          FulfillmentGroup cloned = createResponse.getClone();                                                      
 796          cloned.setAddress(address == null ? null : address.createOrRetrieveCopyInstance(context).getClone());     
 797          cloned.setDeliveryInstruction(deliveryInstruction);                                                       
 798          cloned.setFulfillmentOption(fulfillmentOption);                                                           
 799          cloned.setFulfillmentPrice(fulfillmentPrice == null ? null : new Money(fulfillmentPrice));                
 800          cloned.setIsShippingPriceTaxable(isShippingPriceTaxable == null ? null : isShippingPriceTaxable);         
 801          cloned.setMerchandiseTotal(merchandiseTotal == null ? null : new Money(merchandiseTotal));                
 802          cloned.setRetailFulfillmentPrice(fulfillmentPrice == null ? null : new Money(fulfillmentPrice));          
 803          cloneTaxDetails(context, cloned);                                                                         
 804          cloned.setTotalItemTax(totalItemTax == null ? null : new Money(totalItemTax));                            
 805          cloned.setTotalFulfillmentGroupTax(totalFulfillmentGroupTax == null ? null : new Money(totalFulfillmentGroðŸ”µ
 806          cloned.setTotalFeeTax(totalFeeTax == null ? null : new Money(totalFeeTax));                               
 807          cloned.setTotalTax(totalTax == null ? null : new Money(totalTax));                                        
 808          cloned.setRetailFulfillmentPrice(retailFulfillmentPrice == null ? null : new Money(retailFulfillmentPrice)ðŸ”µ
 809          cloned.setSaleFulfillmentPrice(saleFulfillmentPrice == null ? null : new Money(saleFulfillmentPrice));    
 810          cloned.setTotal(total == null ? null : new Money(total));                                                 
 811          cloned.setOrder(order);                                                                                   
 812          cloned.setPrimary(primary);                                                                               
 813          cloned.setType(getType());                                                                                
 814          for (FulfillmentGroupItem fgi: fulfillmentGroupItems) {                                                   
 815              FulfillmentGroupItem fulfillmentGroupItem = fgi.createOrRetrieveCopyInstance(context).getClone();     
 816              fulfillmentGroupItem.setFulfillmentGroup(cloned);                                                     
 817              cloned.getFulfillmentGroupItems().add(fulfillmentGroupItem);                                          
 818          }                                                                                                         
 819          return  createResponse;                                                                                   
 820      }                                                                                                             
 821                                                                                                                    
 822      protected void cloneTaxDetails(MultiTenantCopyContext context, FulfillmentGroup cloned) throws CloneNotSupportðŸ”µ
 823          for (TaxDetail taxDetail : getTaxes()) {                                                                  
 824              TaxDetail clonedTaxDetail = taxDetail.createOrRetrieveCopyInstance(context).getClone();               
 825              cloned.getTaxes().add(clonedTaxDetail);                                                               
 826          }                                                                                                         
 827      }

 829      @Override                                                                                                     
 830      public boolean equals(Object obj) {                                                                           
 831          if (this == obj) {                                                                                        
 832              return true;                                                                                          
 833          }                                                                                                         
 834          if (obj == null) {                                                                                        
 835              return false;                                                                                         
 836          }                                                                                                         
 837          if (!getClass().isAssignableFrom(obj.getClass())) {                                                       
 838              return false;                                                                                         
 839          }                                                                                                         
 840          FulfillmentGroupImpl other = (FulfillmentGroupImpl) obj;                                                  
 841                                                                                                                    
 842          if (id != null && other.id != null) {                                                                     
 843              return id.equals(other.id);                                                                           
 844          }                                                                                                         
 845                                                                                                                    
 846          if (address == null) {                                                                                    
 847              if (other.address != null) {                                                                          
 848                  return false;                                                                                     
 849              }                                                                                                     
 850          } else if (!address.equals(other.address)) {                                                              
 851              return false;                                                                                         
 852          }                                                                                                         
 853          if (fulfillmentGroupItems == null) {                                                                      
 854              if (other.fulfillmentGroupItems != null) {                                                            
 855                  return false;                                                                                     
 856              }                                                                                                     
 857          } else if (!fulfillmentGroupItems.equals(other.fulfillmentGroupItems)) {                                  
 858              return false;                                                                                         
 859          }                                                                                                         
 860          return true;                                                                                              
 861      }

 370      @Override                                                                                                     
 371      public List<DiscreteOrderItem> getDiscreteOrderItems() {                                                      
 372          List<DiscreteOrderItem> discreteOrderItems = new ArrayList<DiscreteOrderItem>();                          
 373          for (FulfillmentGroupItem fgItem : fulfillmentGroupItems) {                                               
 374              OrderItem orderItem = fgItem.getOrderItem();                                                          
 375              if (orderItem instanceof BundleOrderItem) {                                                           
 376                  BundleOrderItemImpl bundleOrderItem = (BundleOrderItemImpl)orderItem;                             
 377                  for (DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem : bundleOrderItem.getDiscreteOrderItems()) {             
 378                      discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                                    
 379                  }                                                                                                 
 380              } else if (orderItem instanceof DiscreteOrderItem) {                                                  
 381                  DiscreteOrderItem discreteOrderItem = (DiscreteOrderItem)orderItem;                               
 382                  discreteOrderItems.add(discreteOrderItem);                                                        
 383              }                                                                                                     
 384          }                                                                                                         
 385          return discreteOrderItems;                                                                                
 386      }

 780      @Override                                                                                                     
 781      public int hashCode() {                                                                                       
 782          final int prime = 31;                                                                                     
 783          int result = 1;                                                                                           
 784          result = prime * result + ((address == null) ? 0 : address.hashCode());                                   
 785          result = prime * result + ((fulfillmentGroupItems == null) ? 0 : fulfillmentGroupItems.hashCode());       
 786          return result;

 789      @Override                                                                                                     
 790      public <G extends FulfillmentGroup> CreateResponse<G> createOrRetrieveCopyInstance(MultiTenantCopyContext contðŸ”µ
 791          CreateResponse<G> createResponse = context.createOrRetrieveCopyInstance(this);                            
 792          if (createResponse.isAlreadyPopulated()) {                                                                
 793              return createResponse;                                                                                
 794          }                                                                                                         
 795          FulfillmentGroup cloned = createResponse.getClone();                                                      
 796          cloned.setAddress(address == null ? null : address.createOrRetrieveCopyInstance(context).getClone());     
 797          cloned.setDeliveryInstruction(deliveryInstruction);                                                       
 798          cloned.setFulfillmentOption(fulfillmentOption);

 829      @Override                                                                                                     
 830      public boolean equals(Object obj) {                                                                           
 831          if (this == obj) {                                                                                        
 832              return true;                                                                                          
 833          }                                                                                                         
 834          if (obj == null) {                                                                                        
 835              return false;                                                                                         
 836          }                                                                                                         
 837          if (!getClass().isAssignableFrom(obj.getClass())) {                                                       
 838              return false;                                                                                         
 839          }                                                                                                         
 840          FulfillmentGroupImpl other = (FulfillmentGroupImpl) obj;                                                  
 841                                                                                                                    
 842          if (id != null && other.id != null) {                                                                     
 843              return id.equals(other.id);                                                                           
 844          }                                                                                                         
 845                                                                                                                    
 846          if (address == null) {                                                                                    
 847              if (other.address != null) {                                                                          
 848                  return false;                                                                                     
 849              }                                                                                                     
 850          } else if (!address.equals(other.address)) {                                                              
 851              return false;                                                                                         
 852          }                                                                                                         
 853          if (fulfillmentGroupItems == null) {                                                                      
 854              if (other.fulfillmentGroupItems != null) {                                                            
 855                  return false;                                                                                     
 856              }                                                                                                     
 857          } else if (!fulfillmentGroupItems.equals(other.fulfillmentGroupItems)) {                                  
 858              return false;                                                                                         
 859          }                                                                                                         
 860          return true;                                                                                              
 861      }
